---
title: Sichuan Honey-Glazed Pork Rissoles with Roast Veggie & Corn Toss
description: Pork rissoles are a crowd-pleasing dinner winner, but when you add our All-American spice blend and toss them in sriracha and
honey, they’re even harder to refuse! This plate also includes a serving of colourful roast veggies for a rainbow of delights.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65bc7e6b03a59291195203b2-a5df44cf.jpeg
